      "span_text": "Based on the results of L. Zhang et al., in which changes in plasma miRNA abundance were reported in mice within 3-6 h of food intake (rice), [CITATION_1] we drew blood at 1, 4, and 12 h postprandial time points for comparison with an overnight fasting, pre-intake time point."
